# Echoes of Conquest

A turn-based combat RPG built in C#. Create a hero, choose your class, and fight your way through a gauntlet of enemies.

## Features

- Three playable classes: Fighter, Rogue, and Wizard
- Turn-based combat with dice rolls for attack and damage
- Inventory system with health potions and weapons
- Five enemy encounters: Goblin, Orc, Skeleton, Dark Mage, and Dragon

## How to Play

1. Enter your character's name and choose a class
2. In each combat encounter, choose to [A]ttack or use an [I]tem
3. Defeat all five enemies to win

## Requirements

- .NET 8 or later
